The paper deals with a problem of distributed algorithm for mobile robots, which is a typical topic in the field of Multi-Agent Systems (MAS) and Robotics (RO). Therefore, cs.MA and cs.RO are the most likely categories. The problem also involves coordination and communication among the robots, which are typical topics in Distributed Computing (DC) and Distributed Systems (DS). Hence, cs.DC and cs.DS are also likely categories. Finally, the problem involves designing algorithms that ensure certain properties, which is a typical topic in Control Systems (SY). Therefore, cs.SY is also a likely category.
